Description:
Before you lie the unfathomable depths of the abyssal trench. 

However, something shiny catches your attention, almost supernaturally. 

You could reach it, and who knows what else might be down there, but venturing so deep will undoubtedly test your ability to withstand the harshness of the ocean's depths.
DescriptionAction: Are you willing to take the risk?
